## Cross-Functional Coordination Workflow

- [ ] 1. Map stakeholders: Identify all teams and key contacts
- [ ] 2. Define dependencies: What does each team need from others?
- [ ] 3. Establish cadences: Regular sync meetings, update formats
- [ ] 4. Set communication rules: How updates are shared, who escalates to whom
- [ ] 5. Track dependencies: Monitor handoffs and blockers
- [ ] 6. Resolve conflicts: Align on priority when teams conflict
- [ ] 7. Close the loop: Confirm when dependencies are fulfilled

## Key Inputs
- Teams involved: {{teams}}
- Project scope: {{project_scope}}
- Key dependencies: {{dependencies}}
- Communication cadence: {{cadence}}
